                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "8d79995ed2b393c12a27b3db4d500b51",
                "text": "Azarketi are an offshoot of humans adapted to live in aquatic communities. They have gills, webbed digits, and small fins, and they can survive in or out of water.",
                "classes": [
                    "trait"
                ]
            },
            {
